{"image_id": "BXP_2005_page_42", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "We face possible adverse changes in tax laws.", "bbox": [162.5, 157.8, 554.1, 178.7]}, {"text": "From time to time changes in state and local tax laws or regulations are enacted, which may result in an", "bbox": [204.2, 194.6, 1069.2, 215.5]}, {"text": "increase in our tax liability. A shortfall in tax revenues for states and municipalities in which we operate may", "bbox": [162.5, 219.6, 1073.4, 240.5]}, {"text": "lead to an increase in the frequency and size of such changes. If such changes occur, we may be required to pay", "bbox": [162.5, 244.6, 1093.7, 265.5]}, {"text": "additional taxes on our assets or income. These increased tax costs could adversely affect our financial condition", "bbox": [162.5, 269.6, 1103.3, 290.5]}, {"text": "and results of operations and the amount of cash available for payment of dividends.", "bbox": [162.5, 294.6, 867.2, 315.5]}, {"text": "We face possible state and local tax audits.", "bbox": [162.5, 354.3, 528.7, 375.1]}, {"text": "Because we are organized and qualify as a REIT, we are generally not subject to federal income taxes, but", "bbox": [204.2, 391.1, 1090.7, 411.9]}, {"text": "are subject to certain state and local taxes. In the normal course of business, certain entities through which we", "bbox": [162.5, 416.1, 1078.6, 436.9]}, {"text": "own real estate either have undergone, or are currently undergoing, tax audits. Although we believe that we have", "bbox": [162.5, 441.1, 1103.5, 461.9]}, {"text": "substantial arguments in favor of our positions in the ongoing audits, in some instances there is no controlling", "bbox": [162.5, 466.1, 1078.4, 486.9]}, {"text": "precedent or interpretive guidance on the specific point at issue. Collectively, tax deficiency notices received to", "bbox": [162.5, 491.1, 1093.1, 511.9]}, {"text": "date from the jurisdictions conducting the ongoing audits have not been material. However, there can be no", "bbox": [162.5, 516.1, 1058.6, 536.9]}, {"text": "assurance that future audits will not occur with increased frequency or that the ultimate result of such audits will", "bbox": [162.5, 541.1, 1100.7, 561.9]}, {"text": "not have a material adverse effect on our results of operations.", "bbox": [162.5, 566.1, 682.4, 586.9]}, {"text": "Item 1B.", "bbox": [162.5, 625.8, 239.0, 646.6]}, {"text": "Unresolved Staff Comments.", "bbox": [256.2, 625.8, 502.3, 646.6]}, {"text": "None.", "bbox": [204.2, 662.5, 254.5, 683.4]}, {"text": "Item 2.", "bbox": [162.5, 722.2, 225.1, 743.1]}, {"text": "Properties", "bbox": [256.2, 722.2, 344.2, 743.1]}, {"text": "At December 31, 2005, our portfolio consisted of 121 properties totaling 42.0 million net rentable square", "bbox": [204.2, 759.0, 1080.5, 779.8]}, {"text": "feet. Our properties consisted of (1) 117 office properties, comprised of 100 Class A office buildings, including 3", "bbox": [162.5, 784.0, 1108.6, 804.8]}, {"text": "properties under construction and 17 properties that support both office and technical uses, (2) two retail", "bbox": [162.5, 809.0, 1034.3, 829.8]}, {"text": "properties and (3) two hotels. In addition, we own or control 527.1 acres of land for future development. The", "bbox": [162.5, 834.0, 1071.1, 854.8]}, {"text": "table set forth below shows information relating to the properties we owned, or in which we had an ownership", "bbox": [162.5, 859.0, 1081.9, 879.8]}, {"text": "interest, at December 31, 2005. Information relating to properties owned by the Value-Added Fund is not", "bbox": [162.5, 884.0, 1042.1, 904.8]}, {"text": "included in our portfolio information tables or any other portfolio level statistics because the Value-Added Fund", "bbox": [162.5, 909.0, 1100.0, 929.8]}, {"text": "invests in assets within our existing markets that have deficiencies in property characteristics which provide an", "bbox": [162.5, 934.0, 1088.6, 954.8]}, {"text": "opportunity to create value through repositioning, refurbishment or renovation. We therefore believe including", "bbox": [162.5, 959.0, 1086.5, 979.8]}, {"text": "such information in our portfolio tables and statistics would render the portfolio information less useful to", "bbox": [162.5, 984.0, 1047.0, 1004.8]}, {"text": "investors. Information relating to the Value-Added Fund is set forth below separately.", "bbox": [162.5, 1009.0, 879.3, 1029.8]}, {"text": "Properties", "bbox": [183.3, 1101.9, 257.4, 1118.6]}, {"text": "Location", "bbox": [713.5, 1101.9, 776.5, 1118.6]}, {"text": "%", "bbox": [876.3, 1085.2, 892.9, 1101.9]}, {"text": "Leased", "bbox": [859.6, 1101.9, 909.6, 1118.6]}, {"text": "Number", "bbox": [944.9, 1068.6, 1004.1, 1085.2]}, {"text": "of", "bbox": [967.6, 1085.2, 981.5, 1101.9]}, {"text": "Buildings", "bbox": [940.8, 1101.9, 1008.4, 1118.6]}, {"text": "Net", "bbox": [1058.3, 1051.9, 1083.3, 1068.6]}, {"text": "Rentable", "bbox": [1038.9, 1068.6, 1102.7, 1085.2]}, {"text": "Square", "bbox": [1045.3, 1085.2, 1096.2, 1101.9]}, {"text": "Feet", "bbox": [1055.5, 1101.9, 1086.0, 1118.6]}, {"text": "Class A Office", "bbox": [183.3, 1132.2, 307.1, 1153.1]}, {"text": "399 Park Avenue . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [225.0, 1157.2, 630.3, 1178.1]}, {"text": "New York, NY", "bbox": [651.1, 1157.2, 779.0, 1178.1]}, {"text": "100.0%", "bbox": [861.1, 1157.2, 925.3, 1178.1]}, {"text": "1", "bbox": [969.4, 1157.2, 979.8, 1178.1]}, {"text": "1,686,495", "bbox": [1029.2, 1157.2, 1112.4, 1178.1]}, {"text": "Citigroup Center . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [225.0, 1182.2, 630.3, 1203.1]}, {"text": "New York, NY", "bbox": [651.1, 1182.2, 779.0, 1203.1]}, {"text": "96.6%", "bbox": [871.5, 1182.2, 925.3, 1203.1]}, {"text": "1", "bbox": [969.3, 1182.2, 979.7, 1203.1]}, {"text": "1,569,022", "bbox": [1029.1, 1182.2, 1112.5, 1203.1]}, {"text": "Times Square Tower . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [225.0, 1207.2, 630.3, 1228.1]}, {"text": "New York, NY"